------------------------------------------------------------------------
                      The Ministry of Silly Vaults
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Various utility scripts that generate vaults presumably for use in a
roguelike. For example, the radius 2 vaults generated by 'circulator',
with the usual convention that '.' is a floor tile and '#' a wall.

       ..#..  ..#..  ..#..  ..#..  .###.  .###.  .###.
       .....  .....  #...#  .#.#.  #...#  #...#  ##.##
       .....  #...#  .....  #...#  .....  #...#  #...#
       .....  .....  #...#  .#.#.  #...#  #...#  ##.##
       ..#..  ..#..  ..#..  ..#..  .###.  .###.  .###.

Usage & Utilities

    make depend
      will install any required perl module dependencies, assuming perl
      and App::cpanminus are installed

    circulator
      generates "circular" vaults of a given radius, to the extent not-
      square terminal fonts support that

        ./circulator 7

    spiralfoo
      spirals, or something akin. code will require tweaking
